<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage xmlns="http://xamarin.com/schemas/2014/forms"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml" xmlns:umelusitrack="clr-namespace:UMelusiTrack" x:DataType="umelusitrack:MainPage2"
             x:Class="UMelusiTrack.FAQ">
    <ContentPage.Content>
        <StackLayout>
            <Label Text="Instructions"
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="30"/>
            <Label Text="1.	Farmers should acquire necessary equipment through Umalusi. This includes the physical trackers, the collar and an ear tag."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17" />
            <Label Text="2.	Farmers need to identify the livestock which they wish to track and monitor."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17" />
            <Label Text="3.	Farmers need to select the most comfortable area around the neck of the cow."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17" />
            <Label Text="4.	Tie belt firmly but comfortably around neck of livestock and activate the tracker."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17"/>
            <Label Text="5.	Synchronize each to collar-tracker to the app immediately and register the cow with its tag number and species via Umalusi application."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17"/>
            <Label Text="6.	Farmers should set up farm boundaries/geo-fence boundaries and areas which they wish to monitor via the Umalusi app."
                VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand" 
                HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="17" />
        </StackLayout>
    </ContentPage.Content>
</ContentPage>